'''Geoff Leesley''' (born June 1, 1949) is an English actor. He has appeared in television series such as ''The Bill'', ''Coronation Street'', ''Little Britain'', ''Midsomer Murders'', ''Casualty'', ''Eastenders'', ''Law &amp; Order: UK'', ''White Heat'', ''Doctors'' and ''Holby City'' as well as the film ''Wimbledon''.

In ''[[Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series]]'', he voices Lord [[Ludd Whitehill]] and [[Norren]].
